text: "Bohemian Like You" is a 2000 song by American alternative rock band The Dandy Warhols and is the second single from their third studio album Thirteen Tales from Urban Bohemia. It went to number 1 in Portugal, number 5 in the United Kingdom, Greece and Italy, number 17 in Ireland and number 19 in the Netherlands. ==Track listings== ===Original 2000 release=== ===2001 re- release=== ==References== Category:2000 songs Category:The Dandy Warhols songs Category:Power pop songs
